  "categorySlug": "compliance-server-how-to-videos",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to use the Report Editor Page</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">The Report Editor page allows the administrator to customize the Notifications Report, Notification Mails, and Analytics Mails</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><div class=\"hs-callout-type-note\" data-hs-callout-type=\"note\">\n<ul>\n<li>By default, only users with <em><strong>Admin</strong></em> or <em><strong>Admin Lite</strong></em> roles have access to the Report Editor.</li>\n<li>To have access, the user must have a role with the \"Report Managet / View Report Production\" enabled.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>For a report to be accessible in the \"Report Editor\" Meny, the policy that the report is based on must have the status <em><strong>Open</strong></em>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The report page can be accessed via the back right menu and is used to control the look and feel of the Compliance Reports and the Notification Mails.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"1888\" style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=3418&amp;height=1888&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png\" width=\"3418\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=1709&amp;height=944&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 1709w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=3418&amp;height=1888&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 3418w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=5127&amp;height=2832&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 5127w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=6836&amp;height=3776&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 6836w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=8545&amp;height=4720&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 8545w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png?width=10254&amp;height=5664&amp;name=image-png-Jul-31-2024-09-46-12-4283-AM.png 10254w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3418px) 100vw, 3418px\"></p>\n<p>The structure of the report page is divided into four tabs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Report tab</strong>: Control the date/time of the send-out data for notification, as well as the Compliance Report text and features</li>\n<li><strong>Subscriber</strong>: Controls the content of the Notification Mail and well as enables the send out to Subscribers. (Subscribers is the term used for any end-user that have non-compliant data and must be notified)&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>Analytics</strong>: Controls who should get the Analytics report &amp; the text in the mail for the Analytics Report&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>Notifications</strong>: This is a list of all notifications, including who has received them. It enables an individual resend for each notificaion</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/how-to-use-the-repot-tab"
}